comments.content:
I could not reproduce this bug.  I am using the nova master branch and was able to run the test case successfully:

$ ./run_tests.sh test_neutronv2.TestNeutronv2.test_allocate_floating_ip_exhausted_fail
Running `tools/with_venv.sh python -m nova.openstack.common.lockutils python setup.py testr --testr-args='--subunit --concurrency 0  test_neutronv2.TestNeutronv2.test_allocate_floating_ip_exhausted_fail'`
nova.tests.network.test_neutronv2.TestNeutronv2
